usage: cim_installer
usage: cim_installer git <repo>

cim_installer -- Install CIM into the home directory.
                 Add a snipet into the initialization script of current shell.

cim_installer git <repo> -- instead of retrieving CIM from the predefined official repository,
                            get the archive from any specified git repository, using git-archive feature.
                            This is only for the debugging purpose.



